# Deploying to Vercel

1. Push this repo to GitHub.
2. Go to https://vercel.com/new and import your repository.
3. Set build command: `npm run build`, output directory: (leave empty — Next.js App Router is detected automatically).
4. Add Environment Variables:
   - `YOUTUBE_API_KEY` (optional, for dynamic embeds)
   - `YOUTUBE_CHANNEL_ID` (optional)
5. Deploy.
